With Tao under heaven Stray horses fertilize the fields. Without Tao under
 heaven Warhorses are bred at the frontier.
There is no greater calamity Than not knowing what is enough. There is no
 greater fault Than desire for success.
Therefore, Knowing that enough is enough Is always Enough.
